{"tid":403893,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有無人係有玩War3 LOL？","createTime":"2017-09-17T14:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T13:07:36.000Z","uid":102938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b02528a37b047ef6fcb02e48603f9e58d2478529","tid":403893,"uid":102938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:24:24.000Z","msg":"以前中學一大班人玩 之後每過一年 身邊就愈來愈少朋友玩<br />\nWar3由小學2005年左右開始玩 但玩到2011年漸漸被LOL取代<br />\n2012年LOL TPA拎冠軍 正式踏入LOL年代 當年晚晚上LOL<br />\n可以有幾十位位好友 (真人識 唔係完場亂加)<br />\n但到近年 真心每晚見得幾位好友 真係有小小傷感<br />\n所以想問有無人會想得閒玩下War3 LOL 唔洗神手 開心玩就得"},{"pid":"e1bda6b97bba305002e0d838a114339a9c458800","tid":403893,"uid":130157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:29:42.000Z","msg":"不如出黎玩board game 好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b33c924317faaf130f80f55d5526c5ec46d7ca1","tid":403893,"uid":91502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T19:49:21.000Z","msg":"不如去扑野好過"},{"pid":"8eb3c9f42de8ced135e2206a174f15592b342a68","tid":403893,"uid":141496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T20:15:35.000Z","msg":"信長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f4815398eb48e6709551e4ce0bbbd6e492fc5b","tid":403893,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T20:21:11.000Z","msg":"War3小遊戲圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94111c2352e3ec7873ad91f76ba12b9dbc0e2c58","tid":403893,"uid":102938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:47:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如出黎玩board game 好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前中學年代同大專/大學年代都仲有組一大班人去朋友家玩卡game<br />\n好多唔同類型 最經典就一定係三國殺啦 仲有其他十幾種<br />\n但之後個個投身社會返工都唔得閒 完全組唔到人玩 主因夾唔到假期<br />\n<br />\nWar3真係經典 樓上有興趣可以留TG一齊玩 LOL都得"},{"pid":"262c15a45d808c9f3d883a71216acaf6816ec256","tid":403893,"uid":102938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:44:38.000Z","msg":"見到好友得1人上線真係悲哀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd65f1e7eaded73db71e23a18b332b2b55fbff5f","tid":403893,"uid":83420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:49:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab9b35ab66c5104527189ed67da52515615c0052","tid":403893,"uid":102938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T14:50:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講起又講<br />\n一年冇上玩信，依排想玩返<br />\n入到vlan有150人，開game但唔見有場<br />\nin game等場個頁唔知點解<br />\n連我自己個vlan名都見唔到<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打知咩事？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nVLAN依排有問題？"},{"pid":"4b1e70472be535c7c8ad1a7da43308d38dfc0aae","tid":403893,"uid":102938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T10:03:48.000Z","msg":"有無人有興趣一齊玩"},{"pid":"283b1384f4f7124327fc8d3972d0caba90dfb861","tid":403893,"uid":83420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T10:59:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1bf731eb13bfd3c0152184678ed4abdbe700ba6f","tid":403893,"uid":61724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T13:07:36.000Z","msg":"VLAN用1.28你地緊係見唔到場啦 都無更新"}]}